  "article": {
    "published_at": "2026-04-01T14:47:20.000000Z",
    "id": 2039353929562231300,
    "id_str": "2039353929562231194",
    "title": "I Launched 3 Startups in 7 Days. Here's how to Go Viral on X.",
    "preview_text": "We launched 3 startups on X in 1 week. 5.2M+ views. Hundreds of US sales/demos.\nGarry Tan and Gokul Rajaram & more in the replies.\nHere's what we shipped this week at @atomikgrowth \n#1 MaveHealth",
    "cover_url": "https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HE1F54daoAEIybc.jpg",
    "content_state": {
      "blocks": [
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "31k3h",
          "text": "We launched 3 startups on X in 1 week. 5.2M+ views. Hundreds of US sales/demos.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "aq9i4",
          "text": "Garry Tan and Gokul Rajaram & more in the replies.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 36,
                "text": "atomikgrowth",
                "toIndex": 49
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4fajg",
          "text": "Here's what we shipped this week at @atomikgrowth ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 15,
                "text": "thatssodhawal",
                "toIndex": 29
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 15,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            },
            {
              "length": 40,
              "offset": 29,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "4sec7",
          "text": "#1 MaveHealth (@thatssodhawal)[Consumer Health Tech/$2.1M Seed Round]",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "685jo",
          "text": "MaveHealth makes a wearable headset for focus, mood, and sleep, but it wasn’t getting the traction it deserved.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9utll",
          "text": "The goal was to put MaveHealth on the radar of biohackers, productivity nerds, and investors on X.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "9ahan",
          "text": "Drive awareness and sales for a consumer hardware product that most of the internet had never heard of.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 17,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "anjan",
          "text": "Impression target: 1M.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "87q5r",
          "text": "Where Atomik came in: X amplification and relevant distribution with sales.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "6lg0e",
          "text": "We reverse-engineered who the productivity nerds and biohacker bros actually trust on X, then collaborated with them on launch amplification.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 10,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            },
            {
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 12,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "alvd6",
          "text": "Output:  \n1. 2.5M+ impressions (outperformed target) \n2. Increased awareness + traction (2.5M views)\n3. Limited batches sold out in 36 hours \n4. US sales in the hundreds",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 0,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a0otu",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 16,
                "text": "pritopian",
                "toIndex": 26
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 59,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "fognm",
          "text": "Launch 2: Lica (@pritopian) [Foundational Model for Design]",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "a3ek7",
          "text": "Lica is a foundational image-gen model that lets you edit generations without regenerating everything.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2h6jq",
          "text": "They wanted to launch on X and put it in front of builders, designers, and the startup crowd.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4idqv",
          "text": "We handled the launch video and influencer amplification.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f2hvh",
          "text": "Our AI studio built the launch video ft. Bernie Sanders.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7e2qj",
          "text": "He was already trending on X that week off his Claude post, so we hijacked the meme as the hook.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 1,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c6mmf",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2jrgf",
          "text": "Results:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c16q1",
          "text": "1.4M+ views (outperformed target)",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "7vn43",
          "text": "Engagement from the AI builder community",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "78lpo",
          "text": "Post drove signups directly from X",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 2,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "3207t",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 20,
                "text": "KaranVaidya6",
                "toIndex": 33
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 76,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "1u3l2",
          "text": "Launch 3: Composio (@KaranVaidya6) [AI Agent Infrastructure / $29M Series A]",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "1t8fb",
          "text": "Composio builds the infrastructure that connects AI agents to 1,000+ apps and they needed to launch their Universal CLI right into the middle of the MCP vs CLI debate happening on dev X.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c31ie",
          "text": "The MCP vs CLI debate was already a holy war on X.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f9fa2",
          "text": "Most companies would post a product announcement and hope to catch the wave. We made the wave.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 0,
                "text": "itsaqd",
                "toIndex": 7
              },
              {
                "fromIndex": 10,
                "text": "juliafedorin",
                "toIndex": 23
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "36uqm",
          "text": "@itsaqd & @juliafedorin grabbed a camera crew. Hit the streets of SF.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "4mvj4",
          "text": "One question to strangers: MCP or CLI?",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 3,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "e7mji",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 65,
                "text": "garrytan",
                "toIndex": 74
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "924ot",
          "text": "You know the buzz hit right, when SF's unofficial mayor co-signs @garrytan ",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 4,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "2vp74",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": {
            "mentions": [
              {
                "fromIndex": 0,
                "text": "gokulr",
                "toIndex": 7
              }
            ]
          },
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "412l1",
          "text": "@gokulr also jumped in.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 5,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "d4tk7",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 8,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "37uum",
          "text": "Results:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "euvct",
          "text": "1.9M+ views (outperformed target)",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "fdfl1",
          "text": "Garry Tan and Gokul Rajaram both engaging organically",
          "type": "unordered-list-item"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [
            {
              "key": 6,
              "length": 1,
              "offset": 0
            }
          ],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "e6hpl",
          "text": " ",
          "type": "atomic"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [
            {
              "length": 60,
              "offset": 0,
              "style": "Bold"
            }
          ],
          "key": "dif5j",
          "text": "What we've learned shipping launches back-to-back in 1 week:",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "f2ujn",
          "text": "- The story is the strategy. Great story/content beats hype every time!",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "48pbt",
          "text": "- Don't play it safe, bring personality, bring honesty, show a little more of yourself than feels comfortable. More debatable topic = More engagement",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "8pl4a",
          "text": "- Amplification means mapping exactly whose feed you need to be in, writing a custom copy for each layer, and timing it so the algorithm sees density, not noise. There's nothing passive about it.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        },
        {
          "data": [],
          "entityRanges": [],
          "inlineStyleRanges": [],
          "key": "c2e7o",
          "text": "- Speed forces clarity. Three launches in one week mean zero room for overthinking. Bias towards action.",
          "type": "unstyled"
        }
      ],
